execution_plan.description: Find chats where every chat member has sent at least one message in that chat.
execution_plan.query: SELECT c.id, c.name, c.description, c.created_at FROM chats c WHERE NOT EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM chat_members cm WHERE cm.chat_id = c.id AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM messages m WHERE m.chat_id = c.id AND m.sended_by = cm.user_id));
